q~Delete old events<br /><span class="small">Check to remove events older than the current date when new event is added.</span>~,
    '54'          => q~Rebuild Birthday list~,
    '56'          => q~Marquee~,
    '57'          => q~XHTML~,
    '58'          => q~Disable YaBBC Tags in the sneak-preview Text?~,
    '59'          => q~Add Event Icon~,
    '60'          => q~Remove Event Icon~,
